## MISUMARU'S MAGATAMA SHOP
*"Craftsmanship is patience made visible."*

**Operator:** Misumaru Tamatsukuri

A jeweler specializing in magatama, rings, amulets, and decorative accessories. Most of her work is purely ornamental — but some pieces have quiet magical properties she considers incidental to good design.

| Item | Price |
|---|---|
| Magatama (decorative) | 5–50gp depending on material |
| Silver Ring | 25gp |
| Carved Bone Amulet | 15gp |
| Polished Stone Pendant | 10gp |
| Jewelry | Variable |

**Commission Work:**
- Custom pieces available on request
- Materials supplied by the player reduce cost significantly
- Delivery time: 1–3 days depending on complexity

**Notes:**
- She has opinions about aesthetics and will share them unprompted
- Can incorporate materials brought from the tower into jewelry (decorative only; see Alice for enchantment)